anonymous%20for%20so%20long%3F%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3ELong%20story.%20Started%20out%20for%20a%20good%20reason.%20Then%20I%20just%20got%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20it.%20No%20big%20secret.%20I'm%20not%20Lord%20Lucan%2C%20and%20you've%20probably%20never%20heard%20of%20me%20anyway.%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EWhat's%20in%20the%20book%3F%20Just%20a%20load%20of%20fucking%20reprints%3F%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3EYes%20and%20no.%20There's%20lots%20of%20archive%20material%20and%20loads%20of%20new%20things%20as%20well%20--%20such%20as%20'Scorch'%20(a%20Heat%20magazine%20parody)%2C%20Daily%20Mail%20Islander%20(a%20version%20of%20the%20Mail%20created%20by%20the%20denizens%20of%20Daily%20Mail%20Island)%20and%20Now%20Biter%20(Nathan%20Barley's%20lifestyle%20magazine).%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EI%20can't%20find%20the%20book%20in%20my%20local%20bookshop!%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3EThey%20tend%20to%20hide%20them%20--%20try%20scouring%20the%20%22Film%20%26amp%3B%20TV%22%20section%20if%20you're%20not%20having%20any%20luck%20in%20%22Humour%22.%20Or%20ask.%20Nicely.%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EI%20spotted%20the%20name%20%22Nathan%20Barley%22%20in%20the%20credits%20of%20%22Dotcomedy%22%20on%20Channel%204.%20How%20come%3F%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3EBeats%20me.%20Someone%20at%20Princess%20Productions%20having%20a%20laugh%2C%20I%20suppose.%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EIs%20there%20a%20TV%20series%20appearing%20on%20E4%20by%20any%20chance%3F%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3EYes%20--%20it%20starts%20on%20December%205th.%20Look%2C%20there's%20some%20info%20here%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22sm_439837.html%3Fmenu%3Dentertainment%22%3EAnanova%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20is%20TVGH%20published%20fortnightly%3F%20Can't%20you%20make%20it%20weekly%3F%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fb%3EMaybe%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20not%20right%20now.%3Cbr%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%22-1%22%20face%3D%22Arial%2CHelvetica%2CUnivers%2CZurich%20BT%22%3